{"tid":432210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"配音員點入行?","createTime":"2017-10-11T10:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T07:53:42.000Z","uid":153276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a47cef663f6f364f0525e7f41a602571f62d5d8d","tid":432210,"uid":153276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:11:21.000Z","msg":"我自己好鐘意睇動畫，所以對配音員依個職業有興趣<br />\n我都search過資料，如果唔入tbb o既話要出去報course讀<br />\n有無知道依行多d o既巴打分享下?<br />\n我仲讀緊yr3，所以最快兩年之後先會去報，但係都想提前了解下<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee70ec87c68c174c41534dfa0100b803840cda52","tid":432210,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"學日文 去日本做聲優把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港？算撚數啦"},{"pid":"aaae35ceb9ceaee7bb4de79401dd46647ee5fea2","tid":432210,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"去tvb"},{"pid":"5250cc5c2032c2addd6a1438482fe5df497a9d89","tid":432210,"uid":153276,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得廣東話配音都好正wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁始終都要有人配音比小朋友睇卡通o既<br />\n我都想做叮噹啊"},{"pid":"e2b8dfc78e9f1ef3cd82126e5832694a2e2df329","tid":432210,"uid":115189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T11:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學日文 去日本做聲優把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港？算撚數啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n實餓死"},{"pid":"83182a3efb118f4d153c311b10ee1e4c4d39981f","tid":432210,"uid":153276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"我自己都幾肯定我有一份時間flexible o既正職，依個係我興趣黎，但係我想真係入行試下"},{"pid":"59e76a7dc705b7efd2002efcb8b595c23fcf41af","tid":432210,"uid":51520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"其實係可以考慮將配音當係兼職架<br />\n不過要小心啲揀導師 因為太多配音員搵唔到食就去教班 <br />\n但係跟佢哋學跟本就得唔到工作機會 <br />\n仲有唔該有心入行要記得唔好為興趣免費配音 咁只會搞死呢個業界 質素同budget只會不停下降  全部都係用啲學生配音又有乜可能會配得好？<br />\n建議你搵導師要搵返啲佢本身係配音導演或者係領班嘅嚟報"},{"pid":"2364e7300dce3b7b8a69aaf863be0d61b7da8b54","tid":432210,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7139eb92af7f70cdd446ffa00fc5d9e514082340","tid":432210,"uid":51520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2364e7300dce3b7b8a69aaf863be0d61b7da8b54","tid":432210,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59e76a7dc705b7efd2002efcb8b595c23fcf41af","tid":432210,"uid":51520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"其實係可以考慮將配音當係兼職架<br />\n不過要小心啲揀導師 因為太多配音員搵唔到食就去教班 <br />\n但係跟佢哋學跟本就得唔到工作機會 <br />\n仲有唔該有心入行要記得唔好為興趣免費配音 咁只會搞死呢個業界 質素同budget只會不停下降  全部都係用啲學生配音又有乜可能會配得好？<br />\n建議你搵導師要搵返啲佢本身係配音導演或者係領班嘅嚟報"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:20:36.000Z","msg":"你想問邊間 睇吓我答唔答到你啦"},{"pid":"502a668ff8e5e7584029de6bee34a3048df75154","tid":432210,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:42:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb07e7640f20a221b73b14bcdd499cdbd51bfa13","tid":432210,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T16:45:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bca2efdd0bab5b177a8eafaa8f46021b351a2b01","tid":432210,"uid":51520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb07e7640f20a221b73b14bcdd499cdbd51bfa13","tid":432210,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7139eb92af7f70cdd446ffa00fc5d9e514082340","tid":432210,"uid":51520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2364e7300dce3b7b8a69aaf863be0d61b7da8b54","tid":432210,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"re